# Global cleansing standards

- No secrets in source; validate at system boundaries.
- Remove debug `console.log` / prints before handoff unless structured logging is contractually required.
- Run project formatters and linters; fix or justify warnings tied to real defects.
- Keep public types and APIs aligned with `INTERFACE_CONTRACT.md` / predictive maps when those files exist.
